<span id="401">Isidāsī the one, Bodhi the other.<br />
Precept-observers, lovers of Jhāna-rapture,<br />
Learnèd ladies and cleansed from the taint of all worldliness. (401)</span><br />
<span id="402">These having made their round, and broken their fasting,<br />
