<span id="408">My husband's sisters and his brothers too,<br />
And all his kin, scarce were they entered when<br />
I rose in timid zeal and gave them place. (408)</span><br />
<span id="409">And as to food, or boiled or dried, and drink,<br />
That which was to be stored I set aside,<br />
